&nbsp;A two year-old child was found dead in Burford on Saturday afternoon, 5 November 2016. It is believed that the toddler had gone to sleep and was later found dead by family members. Ladysmith Police had cordoned off the area of the one roomed shack, as they worked on getting statements and other evidence to conduct their investigation. At this stage it is not clear how the toddler had died. The two year-old has not been officially identified yet. Ladysmith SAPS will be investigating.